@startuml pipeline-flow
!include c4/C4_Dynamic.puml
!include _style.puml

' TOP-DOWN layout (plain Rel, no LAYOUT_LEFT_RIGHT and no Rel_R/Rel_L direction hints):
' with TWO app lanes, any left-to-right chaining renders a ~5000px strip — measured — which
' both clips at PlantUML's 4096px default (PLANTUML_LIMIT_SIZE; that is exactly how the
' single-app version lost its last node + legend) and embeds as an unreadable sliver.
' Flowing DOWN puts the two lanes side by side per step instead: 1506x2226, no clipping.
' The render also raises PLANTUML_LIMIT_SIZE well above 4096 (Makefile _render_diagrams)
' as a backstop so no diagram can silently clip again.
'
' TWO apps, ONE walk (apps/registry.tsv). The ONLY shared object in the CI intake is the
' EventListener: a SINGLE listener for every app, which label-selects the per-app Trigger CRs
' (vks-airgap-cicd/ci: app), each CEL-filtered on body.repository.name — so a push to one app's
' repo fires ONLY that app's pipeline. The two lanes differ only in the TEST task and the base
' images they build FROM (scripts/lib/apps.sh: app_test_task / app_builder_image / app_runtime_image).

title Pipeline flow — a push to production, inside the air gap (one lane per app)

Person(dev, "Developer")
Container(gitea_java, "Gitea: javawebapp-app", "git repo")
Container(gitea_go, "Gitea: gowebapp-app", "git repo")
Container(el, "Tekton EventListener 'apps'", "ONE listener for every app;\nlabel-selects the per-app Trigger CRs")
Container(pipe_java, "PipelineRun javawebapp-ci", "clone · maven-test · kaniko · write-back")
Container(pipe_go, "PipelineRun gowebapp-ci", "clone · go-test · kaniko · write-back")
ContainerDb(harbor, "Harbor", "OCI registry", $tags="datastore")
Container(dep_java, "Gitea: javawebapp-deploy", "git repo")
Container(dep_go, "Gitea: gowebapp-deploy", "git repo")
Container(argo, "ArgoCD", "one Application per app")
Container(app_java, "javawebapp", "Deployment + Service")
Container(app_go, "gowebapp", "Deployment + Service")

Rel(dev, gitea_java, "1a. git push")
Rel(dev, gitea_go, "1b. git push")
Rel(gitea_java, el, "2a. push webhook")
Rel(gitea_go, el, "2b. push webhook")
Rel(el, pipe_java, "3a. Trigger javawebapp\n(CEL on repository.name)")
Rel(el, pipe_go, "3b. Trigger gowebapp\n(CEL on repository.name)")
Rel(pipe_java, pipe_java, "4a. maven-test, offline\n(deps-baked builder)")
Rel(pipe_go, pipe_go, "4b. go-test\n(stdlib-only)")
Rel(pipe_java, harbor, "5a. kaniko push\napps/javawebapp:<sha>")
Rel(pipe_go, harbor, "5b. kaniko push\napps/gowebapp:<sha>")
Rel(pipe_java, dep_java, "6a. commit the new tag")
Rel(pipe_go, dep_go, "6b. commit the new tag")
Rel(dep_java, argo, "7a. auto-sync")
Rel(dep_go, argo, "7b. auto-sync")
Rel(argo, app_java, "8a. deploy")
Rel(argo, app_go, "8b. deploy")
Rel(harbor, app_java, "pull image")
Rel(harbor, app_go, "pull image")

SHOW_LEGEND()
@enduml
